<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">i would reccomend a 2hs weapon...thats what i use. I have heard past lvl 38 u start using a 1hs. right now i use a 2h practise sword or an exe axe i switch off. the reason i like 2hs better is because u can hit harder.. sure the delay is really bad but you will start to get used to it after a while. i am lvl 20 and i hit for around 48 plus double attack which make me hit for and added value of around 95 or 90 so i love 2hs better than 1hs<p>

