<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Actually, use both.  i used a 2 hander all the way up until lvl 40.  Great!  i can hit harder than everyone else.  whoopie do.  Everyone in my group that was using decent 1handers were doing just as much damage as i was because of the lower delay weapons.  I suppose its a matter of personal preference.  But if you ARE going 2hs.  Get a Mith 2hander, much better weapon than and exe axe, plus the haste stacks with other haste items and spells so you can actually swing like a madman, heh.  its kinda fun to use a 2hs and be hitting almost as fast and as much as someone dual wielding. <br>
errr im straying sorry.  work on all your skills including bash and kick, i didnt do anything but 2hs until 40.  boy did i regret it, when i finally did dual wield i really friggen sucked.  I DW to Yaks and proc like hell, and do quite a bit of damage during a fight.  <p>

Anyway, im straying again.  One last time, keep all your skills relatively close, its personal choice on what you should use.  not everyone plays exactly alike and one person maybe better with 1hs, one with 2hs, and some love 1 and 2 hbs.<p>

just my 2 coppers.<p>

Torind<br>
Warrior of the 45th Cycle<br>
Fennin Ro.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
